title: Tomcat-Thread
visState: {"type":"timelion","title":"Tomcat-Thread","params":{"expression":".es(index='jmxproxybeat-*',metric='sum:bean.value',q='bean.name : \"java.lang:type=Threading\" AND bean.attribute : \"CurrentThreadCpuTime\" AND beat.hostname : \"sethostname\"').label(\"Current Thread CPU Time\"),.es(index='jmxproxybeat-*',metric='sum:bean.value',q='bean.name : \"java.lang:type=Threading\" AND bean.attribute : \"CurrentThreadUserTime\" AND beat.hostname : \"sethostname\"').label(\"Current User CPU Time\"),.es(index='jmxproxybeat-*',metric='sum:bean.value',q='bean.name : \"java.lang:type=Threading\" AND bean.attribute : \"DaemonThreadCount\" AND beat.hostname : \"sethostname\"').label(\"Daemon Thread Count\"),.es(index='jmxproxybeat-*',metric='sum:bean.value',q='bean.name : \"java.lang:type=Threading\" AND bean.attribute : \"ThreadCount\" AND beat.hostname : \"sethostname\"').divide(1048576).label(\"Thread Count\"),.es(index='jmxproxybeat-*',metric='sum:bean.value',q='bean.name : \"java.lang:type=Threading\" AND bean.attribute : \"TotalStartedThreadCount\" AND beat.hostname : \"sethostname\"').label(\"Total Started Thread Count\"),.es(index='jmxproxybeat-*',metric='sum:bean.value',q='bean.name : \"java.lang:type=Threading\" AND bean.attribute : \"PeakThreadCount\" AND beat.hostname : \"sethostname\"').label(\"Total Started Thread Count\")","interval":"10s"}}
